Find your next job with JobServe</a></p><br><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-93c1b71c47a55f2e4375a3e94e8cae03_b.png" data-rawwidth="1339" data-rawheight="583" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1339" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-93c1b71c47a55f2e4375a3e94e8cae03_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1339'%20height='583'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1339" data-rawheight="583" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1339" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-93c1b71c47a55f2e4375a3e94e8cae03_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-93c1b71c47a55f2e4375a3e94e8cae03_b.png"></figure><br><br><p>建议题主和大家多关注<b>行业所需技能、行业动态、公司背景</b>等等，这样在写简历和面试，甚至以后工作的时候都会得心应手很多。</p><br><br><br><b><u>3、香港：</u></b><br><br><br>作者：Kris<br>链接：<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/22547623/answer/126530192" class="internal">本人在内地想去香港工作，请问哪些网站有求职信息？ - Kris 的回答</a><br>来源：知乎<br>著作权归作者所有，转载请联系作者获得授权。<br><br>香港的求职网站主要有以下这些：<br><br><b>1、jobsDB</b><br><br><br><u>网址</u><b>：<a href="http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//hk.jobsdb.com/hk" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">jobsDB – Hong Kong's no. 1 jobs, employment, career and recruitment site</a></b><br><br><u>情况：</u>职位数量多。<br><br><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e6e997ae8a2d46e65c1634758a035a5e_b.png" data-rawwidth="1343" data-rawheight="583" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1343" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e6e997ae8a2d46e65c1634758a035a5e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1343'%20height='583'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1343" data-rawheight="583" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1343" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e6e997ae8a2d46e65c1634758a035a5e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e6e997ae8a2d46e65c1634758a035a5e_b.png"></figure><br><br><b>2、香港劳工处职位空缺。</b><br><br><br><u>网址</u>：<a href="http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www2.jobs.gov.hk/1/0/WebForm/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">勞工</a><a href="http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www2.jobs.gov.hk/1/0/WebForm/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">互</a><a href="http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www2.jobs.gov.hk/1/0/WebForm/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">處動就業服務</a><br><br><br><u>情况：</u>中层或往下的职位较多，且多为小企业。<br><br><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a5f1743b555192f134e1facc5ce5e1d2_b.png" data-rawwidth="1347" data-rawheight="584" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1347" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a5f1743b555192f134e1facc5ce5e1d2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1347'%20height='584'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1347" data-rawheight="584" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1347" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a5f1743b555192f134e1facc5ce5e1d2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a5f1743b555192f134e1facc5ce5e1d2_b.png"></figure><br><br><br><b>3、劳工处展翅青见计划。</b><br><br><br><u>网址</u>：<a href="http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.yes.labour.gov.hk/ypyt/ojt/job_search.aspx" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">勞工處「展翅青見計劃」</a><br><br><u>情况</u>：见习就业空缺数量非常多。<br><br><figure><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-924d5bfa5c2842c1c3301aa21367cc0d_b.png" data-rawwidth="1351" data-rawheight="582" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1351" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-924d5bfa5c2842c1c3301aa21367cc0d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1351'%20height='582'&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-rawwidth="1351" data-rawheight="582" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="13